<br>
Harversters of night, your reign has come to an end, there is a day walker that stalks the night for you and your kin.  I have come back to protect the lands against you and your kind.  I vow that by night, one will die.  Till my last dying breath, I shall take the very essence of that wich you are.  I will show you what hate you feel, you shall feed on it, and then you shall be reunited with your master.  You have been warned, if you walk the day, you nights will be cold.  I stood beside you for a short time, but now my mind has been cleared of the seed that was placed in my heart. I know what I must do to free myself, and your trapped souls.  I shall come in the night as a theif, you shall wake, with Innourk at your side.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;The Shadow&quot;<br>
